---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import LegalArticle from "../components/LegalArticle.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support - Moss"
  description="Support information for the Moss travel companion app."
  bodyClass="legal-page"
>
  <LegalArticle title="Support">
    <p>Moss is developed and supported by Kyle Scudder.</p>

    <h2>Report a bug or request a feature</h2>
    <p>
      Email <a href="mailto:support@getmoss.app">support@getmoss.app</a> with
      what you did, what you expected, and what happened instead.
    </p>

    <h2>Sign-in and account questions</h2>
    <p>
      Moss supports email, Apple, and Google sign-in. Password resets and
      provider account access are handled by the provider you use to sign in.
      For account deletion or data questions, use the in-app account deletion
      flow or email <a href="mailto:support@getmoss.app"
        >support@getmoss.app</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Subscription questions</h2>
    <p>
      Moss subscriptions are managed through your Apple ID. You can manage or
      cancel a subscription in your App Store account settings.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy questions</h2>
    <p>
      Start with the <a href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>. Anything it does not
      answer can be raised by email.
    </p>
  </LegalArticle>
</BaseLayout>
